pageContext.claim: “But there's a tremendous -- there's a vast difference than in bringing -- especially in around 14. Was that 14 or 12? And at that time, nobody had ever even heard of Ebola.”
pageContext.analysis: Researchers were familiar with Ebola. Documented cases of the virus date back to the mid-1970s, according to the World Health Organization. The 2014-2016 outbreak in West Africa was the largest since the virus was first discovered.
